the last modal closed. The next call to
`mission:validate_and_approve` will re-open the modal
regardless of your `requires_reapproval` flag.{{if .PendingReapprovalReason}} Worker reason: {{.PendingReapprovalReason}}.{{end}} Treat this as the user requesting a
fresh look — restate the goal + AC honestly given what was
